Class ConnectedAPAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.SclElementAdapter<SubNetworkAdapter,TConnectedAP>
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.com.ConnectedAPAdapter
public class ConnectedAPAdapter extends SclElementAdapter<SubNetworkAdapter,TConnectedAP>
A representation of the model object ConnectedAP.

The following features are supported:

  • Add TPrivate under this object
  • copy Address And PhysConn From Icd
